    <item>
      <title>当交易员支撑关税时，黄金攀登以加速贸易战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/gold-xauusd-steady-as-traders-brace-for-tariff-hit-to-ramp-up-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金玫瑰是随着交易员为美国提高对中国商品的关税至104％的提示，这一举动预计将对北京进行报复，因为希望可以避免一场残酷的全球贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/gold-xauusd-steady-as-traders-brace-for-tariff-hit-to-ramp-up-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 01:16:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在关税动荡中，亚洲的贸易敏感货币鞭子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/krw-usd-korea-won-falls-to-lowest-since-2009-on-tariff-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德总统特朗普的关税政策的卷入，亚洲的贸易敏感货币围绕着多年的低点，这些政策有可能使全球经济陷入衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/krw-usd-korea-won-falls-to-lowest-since-2009-on-tariff-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 00:24:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
